# SaaS Metrics & Customer Churn Dashboard (Excel Project)

This project simulates the work of a junior data analyst at a B2B SaaS company. The Excel dashboard was designed to help the companyâ€™s leadership monitor key business metrics, spot churn trends, and identify opportunities to improve customer retention and revenue performance.

